{"tid":1362950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感] 那年2014雨傘運動 結果沒有升級","createTime":"2019-07-25T04:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:46:27.000Z","uid":282836,"like":114,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bf39694a68a104335ba86564273b34c42ea4ff96","tid":1362950,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"呢幾日氣氛令我想起2014雨傘運動雙學想升級佔領政總，但當時所有有頭有面淺藍淺黃的人(香港大學校長馬斐森及中文大學校長沈祖堯) 勸年輕人收手，<span style=\"color: red;\">結果沒有升級</span>。<br />\n<br />\n今星期所有大學校長（淺藍），商會（中藍），沈旭暉（淺黃，中產智識份子）都表態，但勸說方向不是抗爭者一方，而是政府一方，代表佢哋知道抗爭者我們的堅定不動搖，<span style=\"color: gold;\">不會再犯2014的錯</span>。呢班中立知道政府已經無牌可以出，要解決這個危機只有政府跪低，否則沒有退讓，尊嚴係人民俾你，唔係你年年考第一就有。<br />\n<br />\n經過兩個月仲有乜未見過，所有潘朵拉的盒子都差不多開晒，政府還有什麼牌剩?"},{"pid":"3d2f40e088a601d8e8d47a424928003a97b1e2c9","tid":1362950,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca1993a65faa76ca4e09f9b4ba72ad0ca4567bc","tid":1362950,"uid":282836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"727 見"},{"pid":"dbe9bb9ef42fdb00d27bdaf5eb14e35ba115f703","tid":1362950,"uid":46370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c1d0029fe98da5d6df8bec273a2d11f17ce15c","tid":1362950,"uid":111934,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"純粹想糾正一樣嘢<br />\n2014 雙學係唔想升級的<br />\n佢地係設計陷害一班真係想用行動升級嘅義士"},{"pid":"16fc160037ee9a0bc719c16c44f7822758347c5a","tid":1362950,"uid":106929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"果陣仲要咩 同政府談判論<br />\n結果係談判都拉晒坐監"},{"pi